article_title: Woman Extricated, Transported to Hospital After Two-Vehicle Crash
article_text:

AT 428 PM MDT

A SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WAS LOCATED NEAR HASWELL

OR 35 MILES NORTHEAST OF NORTH LA JUNTA

MOVING NORTH AT 35 MPH. HAZARD

60 MPH WIND GUSTS AND QUARTER SIZE HAIL. SOURCE

RADAR INDICATED. IMPACT
